'''1-叠氮丙烷'''是一种[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]，化学式为C<sub>3</sub>H<sub>7</sub>N<sub>3</sub>。它可由[[1-溴丙烷|1-溴丙烷]]和[[叠氮化钠|叠氮化钠]]在[[水|H<sub>2</sub>O]]-[[四氢呋喃|THF]]中回流反应得到。<ref name=Swetha />它可用于合成三唑类化合物，如和[[丙炔|丙炔]]反应，得到1-丙基-4-甲基-1''H''-1,2,3-三唑<ref>{{cite journal|journal=The Journal of Physical Chemistry B|volume=118|issue=47|language=en|issn=1520-6106|date=2014-11-26|pages=13609–13620|doi=10.1021/jp506972w|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/jp506972w|title=Toward a Materials Genome Approach for Ionic Liquids: Synthesis Guided by Ab Initio Property Maps|accessdate=2021-01-12|author=Fangyong Yan, Michael Lartey, Kuldeep Jariwala, Sage Bowser, Krishnan Damodaran, Erik Albenze, David R. Luebke, Hunaid B. Nulwala, Berend Smit, Maciej Haranczyk}}</ref>；和[[乙酰乙酸乙酯|乙酰乙酸乙酯]]反应，得到1-丙基-5-甲基-1''H''-1,2,3-三唑-4-甲酸乙酯<ref>{{cite journal|journal=European Journal of Medicinal Chemistry|volume=86|language=en|date=2014-10|pages=87–94|doi=10.1016/j.ejmech.2014.08.029|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0223523414007569|title=Design, synthesis, and fungicidal evaluation of a series of novel 5-methyl-1H-1,2,3-trizole-4-carboxyl amide and ester analogues|accessdate=2021-01-12|author=Zhen-Jun Wang, Yang Gao, Yan-Ling Hou, Cheng Zhang, Shu-Jing Yu, Qiang Bian, Zheng-Ming Li, Wei-Guang Zhao|archive-date=2020-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200212065219/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0223523414007569|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

